                </li>
              </ol>

              <h2>What makes this time zone converter different?</h2>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Multi‑city view:</strong> Compare many cities at once,
                  not just a simple “from–to” conversion.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Interactive timeline:</strong> Drag the slider to
                  explore different hours in a single gesture.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Automatic DST handling:</strong> Uses your browser’s
